OL,3,COil prices falling but households
OL,4,Cstill waiting on fuel support
OL,6,FThe cost of a barrel of oil is now
OL,7,Ftrading under the price it was before
OL,8,Fthe United States launched strikes on
OL,9,FIran.
OL,11,FThe conflict in the Middle East caused
OL,12,Fprices to spike in recent months
OL,13,Fmaking running cars and heating homes
OL,14,Fvery costly.
OL,16,FStruggling households are still
OL,17,Fwaiting for fuel support payments,
OL,18,Fwhich aren't due until the end of the
OL,19,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/2
